         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Göttingen, 16 February 1890. ¶ Esteemed Baron, ¶  ¶ You were so kind as to send me a second collection of your most interesting Australian algae. Permit me to express to you for these as well as for y...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">90.02.16</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">From Gottfried Berthold</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">RB MSS M108b, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">MS is a small card.</p>
               </note>Goettingen den 16. Febr. 1890.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Sehr verehrter Herr Baron!</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sie waren so freundlich, mir eine zweite Sammlung Ihrer hochinteressanten australischen Algen zu uebersenden. Erlauben Sie mir, Ihnen dafür, sowie für Ihre so liebenswürdigen Zeilen, meinen verbindlichsten Dank auszusprechen. Ich hoffe, dass Sie mich bald in die Lage setzen werden, Ihnen auch meinerseits einen kleinen Gegendienst erweisen zu können.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Mit der Versicherung meiner ausgezeichneten Hochachtung</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Ihr ergebenster</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Prof. Dr. G. Berthold.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Göttingen, 16 February 1890.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Esteemed Baron,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>You were so kind as to send me a second collection of your most interesting Australian algae. Permit me to express to you for these as well as for your so gracious lines<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Letter not found.</p>
               </note> my most gracious thanks. I hope that you will soon give me the opportunity to be able to offer a small service to you in return.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>With the assurance of my deepest esteem</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">your most devoted</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Professor Dr G. Berthold.</p>
         </div>
